using leaves and flowers.
State types of flowers.
Use of dichotomous key

petals (hibiscus), fused
petals (morning glory),
keel and standard wing
(pea or bean family), grass
flower.

External and internal

succulent (pome berry,

schizocarp)

internal structures of fruits
and seeds.
